{"to":["alex@erc.org"],"subject":"Visitor Data Summary (January 2022) for ERC Survey","body":"Hi Alex,

As requested, please find below the aggregated visitor data for our office covering January 2022.  No personally identifiable information is included—only overall counts and percentages by business type and visit reason.

Total visitors logged: 85

Breakdown by business type
• Vendors / service providers – 34 (40%)
• Clients / prospective clients – 26 (30%)
• Job applicants – 17 (20%)
• Couriers & deliveries – 8 (10%)

Primary reasons for visit
• Scheduled business meetings – 43 (50%)
• Interviews – 21 (25%)
• Deliveries / pick-ups – 13 (15%)
• Facilities / maintenance support – 8 (10%)

Let me know if you need the figures in a different format or have any follow-up questions.

Best regards,
Jane Doe
Administrative Assistant
"}
